task.summary: Refactored to introduce concept of a player.
Players now have teams, numbers, and ages. The list of league players prints this information in named columns."
Added menu (with the single option to List Players)
Added new packages. Moved user choice concepts into menu.
Improved cohesion of io operations. League has better encapsulation.
Find Player by name and number instead of just name.
TeamMembers are now Comparable so they appear in order by name when listed. Moved name and team back into TeamPlayer and made it an abstract base class.
Setup annotation building properly and added 'Install Lombok Library' and 'Enable Annotation Processing' steps to README
Lomboked the project. Note that SneakyThrows is not supported by the current version of the IntelliJ Lombok plugin.
